reviewText: Vidios are just as I remember them!
old films, however, was as expected, they are great!
Quite possibly politically incorrect, but still entertaining.  I'm so glad the episodes have NOT been remastered.

I bought this for my mom as a birthday gift and she couldn't be happier.  Of course the quality is not what we are all used to, but that is to be expected.  It is perfect.  My mom grew up with this and she loves it!
I wanted to see the "invisible glass" episode. It was not among the 9 videos sent. There should be a listing of episodes available on the DVDs so that we know exactly what  is available.
My husband was more than thrilled with this DVD in both quality and content. Many hours of belly laughter!
